snippet.title: Philips Fidelio L1 Headphones
snippet.description: The beautifully built Philips Fidelio L1 headphones are truly an audiophile's set, sounding sweet with portable speakers and home hi-fi systems.

snippet.title: Tiger versus Lion
snippet.description: Track day cars and Speedway bikes rarely share the same arena but we put these two wild beasts together to see how well they could play with each other.

snippet.title: HTC One M8 specs versus Samsung Galaxy S5, iPhone 5S
snippet.description: The new HTC One rustles up an impressive list of hardware features and a slick new software shell. So far, the 'M8' stands strong against its influential rivals.

snippet.title: Tiger's finest versus Speedway bike
snippet.description: One-off cars are always going to be fun -- especially when they're built in a shed in the east of England and can hit 62mph from rest in less than 3 seconds. It's also fun to put them on sand up against a Speedway rider. As you do.

snippet.title: Samsung Galaxy S5 camera shootout versus HTC One M8, iPhone 5S
snippet.description: Samsung's marquee Galaxy S5 is blazing fast and chock full of new features. But does its 16-megapixel camera have the chops to compete against the HTC One M8 and Apple iPhone 5S?

snippet.title: Microsoft Surface Pro 2 versus the competition
snippet.description: The Surface Pro 2 starts at $899, but an optimal configuration will cost $1,129. What else will that investment buy?

snippet.title: Volkswagen versus iPhone 5
snippet.description: CNET hooks up the iPhone 5 to its biggest accessory: a 2012 Volkswagen Golf R.

snippet.title: Microsoft Surface Pro versus the competition
snippet.description: How does the Surface Pro measure up against other top tablets and laptop alternatives?

snippet.title: Puget Deluge-i L2
snippet.description: We've seen too many speedy, sub-$2,000 gaming PCs this year to get excited by Puget's near-$5,000 desktop, as elaborate as its liquid cooling may be. Its performance doesn't separate it enough from the midrange pack, and it's outclassed by its other high-end competition.
